items.name: case noErr
items.desc: No error occurred but there is no status.

items.name: case err
items.desc: An error occurred that prevented the call from completing.

items.name: case connectionUp
items.desc: The connection appears to be working.

items.name: case connectionIndeterminate
items.desc: The status of the connection is not known.

items.name: case connectionDown
items.desc: The connection does not appear to be working.
